  "title": "Senior Finance Executive (Full Sets / Management Reporting)",
  "description": "<p>Location: Singapore</p><p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>ClearSK operates the ClearSK group of clinics franchised aesthetic and wellness centers across Singapore, Shanghai, Hangzhou, and Kuala Lumpur. As we expand into bio-regenerative healthcare and prepare for an IPO, we are strengthening our finance team. This entry-level role offers hands-on exposure to group operations and AI-enabled finance systems.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>- Maintain full sets of accounts for assigned entities.</p><p>- Handle month-end closings, journal entries, reconciliations, and variance analysis.</p><p>- Prepare monthly management reports and assist in quarterly statutory submissions.</p><p>- Support audit schedules and tax / GST filings.</p><p>- Build and automate Excel templates or simple financial models.</p><p>- Coordinate with regional finance teams on inter-company transactions.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>- Degree in Accounting / Finance from a recognized institution.</p><p>- ACCA / CPA part-qualified advantageous.</p><p>- Fresh graduates welcome; 1–2 years experience preferred.</p><p>- Proficient in Excel and open to learning AI tools and automation.</p><p>- Detail-oriented with strong sense of accountability.</p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><p>Career development under senior finance leaders, medical benefits, and performance bonus.<br /></p><p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Application:</strong></a><br /><br />Complete the form before applying:<br />\n<a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://forms.gle/BANHb1kAYwBY7k6D8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://forms.gle/BANHb1kAYwBY7k6D8</a></p><p>Pay package within the stated range will be commensurate with relevant experience and educational qualifications.</p><p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Please be advised that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</a></p>",
